name: yukinoshita haruno 雪ノ下陽乃(yahari ore no seishun lovecome wa machigatteiru.)
description:
Based on anime S2 and S3.

She has tooooo many clothes and always conbining so I give up to distinguish them. Just try the clothes in the anime. The red coat is very stable though.

I tried so many times but hard to make it perfect. This one maybe the best among them(there are better ones in performance,but this one is stable). It may still have problems when using hires fix in very close range(for example, close-up). The solution is to use a lower denoising strength like 0.6,0.5 or lower when you find the result is not good.

The eye color and hair length is not so stable in lower weight. You can use prompt in that case.

Maybe there is another version, maybe not.
